{"word":"H974 - בָּחַן - bâchan - baw-khan' - Examine - சோதி","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּחַן"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâchan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-khan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Examine / சோதி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சோதி, புடமிடு, பரீட்சி, பரிசோதி, பரீட்சைபார் - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to examine, to try, to prove"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to examine, scrutinize"},{"paragraph":"2) to test, prove, try (used of gold, persons, the heart, a man of God)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be tried, proved"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to make a trial"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>test</i> (especially metals); generally and figuratively to <i>investigate: - </i>examine, prove, tempt, try (trial)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H969 - בָּחֹון - bâchôwn - baw-khone'/969\">H969</a>, <a href=\"#/H971 - בַּחִין - bachîyn - bakh-een'/971\">H971</a>, <a href=\"#/H974 - בָּחַן - bâchan - baw-khan'/974\">H974</a>, <a href=\"#/H975 - בַּחַן - bachan - bakh'-an/975\">H975</a>, <a href=\"#/H976 - בֹּחַן - bôchan - bo'-khan/976\">H976</a>"}]}